dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for Buffalo County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Buffalo_LandUse_2018.gdb.[The zoning classification are defined at the parcel level, but may not fully correspond with parcel boundaries.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.buffalocountywi.gov/185/GIS-Land-Information-Office
